                <p xml:lang="en">The edition is based on the digital transcripts (HTML files wrapped in ePub) available from <ref target="http://shamela.ws/index.php/book/26523" xml:lang="en"> <foreign xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-ijmes">al-maktabat al-shāmila</foreign>
